<h2>What is GBV?</h2>

<ul>
    <li>
        Any harmful act directed at a person which includes physical, emotional, sexual, and financial abuse,
        and is often used to <b>control, harm, or intimidate someone.</b>
    </li>
</ul>

<nav>
    <a href="https://youtu.be/Uhg3cxnwNxc?si=2L65_L2ljrZVzk-U">Click me for more verbal explanation!</a>
</nav>

<p>
    End Gender based violence.<br>
    <b>Gender-Based Violence (GBV)</b> is a serious issue affecting millions of people worldwide.
    It includes physical, emotional, sexual, and financial abuse. Together, we can raise awareness
    and take action to stop it. Ending <b>Gender-Based Violence (GBV)</b> in South Africa is not just a goal—it is an urgent national priority.
</p>

